snippet.textDisplay:
I'll never stop appreciating Coke Studio Pakistan. It's one of the best things I've ever come across in my life and I'm glad I did. It's so innovative, and artistic and displays every song so beautifully, that it leaves me speechless every time I listen to it.
I'll also never stop adoring its ideas, bringing up languages and cultures that are being forgotten by today's generation, and the effort they put into every song. Everyone, including the artists, vocalists, producers, guitarists, make-up artists, wardrobe stylists etc, are doing great and all of them are awesome.
Words will never be enough to describe our feelings towards this song.
Kudos to the team!!

"tum bhi hum hi ho
hum bhi tum hi hai"❤
